# Welcome to Our Dental Career Portal {.unnumbered}

Dr. Phoebe Tsang and team have been providing specialized pediatric care tailored to individual patient needs for almost 20 years. We take pride in being oral health advocates for children aged 0-18.

## Current Opportunities {.unnumbered #current-opportunities}

We are seeking talented professionals for the following positions:

- [Certified Dental Assistant](certified_dental_assistant.qmd)
- [Procedural Sedation Nurse](procedural_sedation_nurse.qmd)
- [Treatment Coordinator](treatment_coordinator.qmd)

::: {.callout-tip}
## Learn More
Click on any position above to view detailed information about:

- Role responsibilities and expectations
- Required qualifications and assessments
- Work environment and culture
- Full-time and part-time options
:::

