## Step 7: Attend Final Hands-On Evaluation {#step-7}

::: {.callout-note}
## Your Path to Team Membership

After your successful interview, selected candidates are invited to our final evaluation day. This is your opportunity to showcase your clinical excellence in our practice!

**Session Availability:**

Practical evaluation sessions are currently available on limited slots:

- **Thursdays** — Limited single sessions
- **Fridays** — Limited single sessions

*Please plan your schedule accordingly. Early scheduling helps secure your preferred evaluation time slot.*
:::

::: {.callout-note}
## Join Our Team on Evaluation Day

During this final evaluation, you will:

- Experience our practice culture firsthand — see what daily work is really like
- Demonstrate your clinical skills in our real healthcare setting
- Interact with our team, patients, and Dr. Phoebe Tsang directly
- Showcase your expertise and commitment to pediatric excellence

**What Makes This Special:**

- Real-world clinical experience in our specialized practice
- Valuable mentorship and feedback from our experienced team
- Direct assessment of team compatibility and cultural fit
- Opportunity to confirm this is the right fit for you
- Unpaid learning experience that counts toward your success

**Progress:** ✓ Step 7 Complete — Congratulations! You've successfully completed all evaluation steps and are now part of our exclusive pediatric dental care team!

*This practical assessment is the final piece of our collaborative evaluation process, ensuring both parties are confident in an ideal fit.*

